Hello, 🙂 do you want to be more productive? Let's do it together! 💪 My name is Enrico, and the idea is simple: we are to do Study With Me Content for hours! 60 or 90 Minutes Style! With Rain sounds, conversations during breaks, and in real-time! I am a Harvard University alumnus (I graduated with a Master's Degree there), and  I will take you with me on my day (live!) Whether you study, work, or just want to be productive, this is the place for you! You guys are my Study Family ❤️, and we are here to support and motivate each other! Let's do this ✨💪

🌟 Buy My Digital Product for Better Productivity and Organization: https://enricovincente.gumroad.com/l/the3Cframework  
This is the 3C Framework - How to Organize your work and studies to achieve the Best Results!

1 ● 📆 Schedule of the Live streams 

Stream Schedule: http://tinyurl.com/StreamScheduleEnrico
I am currently streaming "study with me" content every single day. I am  to work or study for 8-12 hours every day. I might do shorter streams sometimes. Take care of your health, guys, but with that being said, I am CHALLENGING myself and you, too! Do you  accept this challenge? Can you study or be productive every single day?  There is only one way to find out!

2 ● 🤔 FAQs / Frequently Asked Questions

1. Why are you able to study 12 hours every day? How can I do it as well? 
Short answer. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bm2MOzDc0JE  
Complete answer: https://youtu.be/SKdORiujdEI?si=RV34NVVUSy-HbRl5

2. How can you stay focused while studying for long hours? How can I do it too? Here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N3bDBCgepsc :)

3. What do you listen to with your headphones? What music do you like?
I usually listen to the rain sound during the study with me live; the same sound you can hear from this live stream. Other times I listen to some study music. Here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jtFjwUj8_b4

4. How old are you? How tall are you? I was born on the 6th of January 1995. I am 1m and 83cm, 6 feet.

5. Where are you from? Do you study at Harvard? Did you graduate?
I'm from Italy, and I live in a city close to Venice. I studied at Harvard University and graduated there in 2024. Here is the graduation vlog: https://www.youtube.com/shorts/TVo2Ouqf0BU
Here is a video of me studying at Harvard: https://youtu.be/73_bJtalLa4?si=q-_o_RcMFFIqvlJT

6. What are you studying currently? Are you pursuing a degree?
I am currently studying animation and video production. I am not pursuing a degree. I am working on and learning this subject I am very passionate about: Animation.

7. What key Study Tips should I know? 
You MUST know these tips: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wsSAouA_O4M

8. How much time does Enrico sleep?
I average 7-8 hours.

5 ● 👨‍🎓 How I Study & Work

My study session is a 60-minute or 90-minute Pomodoro Timer. Then, there will be a break of 10 minutes (or 9 or 15). During the live study with me, I repeat this for 8-14 hours. This is a double Pomodoro timer (60\10 or 60\9). The Pomodoro technique is very powerful. Breaks are essential to keep the efficiency of your study high. Always take them! I have a timer for all these scenarios. 
I alway study with Discipline ( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2uhMr4eAhQY&t=0s ) and Self-Motivation. ( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HliXs02QPR4&t=0s )
